2026-05-16T05:33:05.2564140Z 273            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T05:33:05.2564469Z 274            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T05:33:05.2564851Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T05:33:05.2565231Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T05:33:05.2565560Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T05:33:05.2565839Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T05:33:05.2566148Z 279            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
